headline: Peloton Accelerates Growth With AI Upgrades & Cross-Training Series
summary: PTON unveils AI-powered coaching, new cross-training equipment and wellness programs as shares climb on strong growth momentum.

headline: Carnival (CCL) Jumps on Record Q3 Profits and Debt Moves Is a New Era Beginning?
summary: Carnival Corporation & plc recently reported record revenues and profits for its third quarter ended August 31, 2025, surpassing pre-pandemic levels and raising its full-year earnings outlook as strong booking trends continue and customer deposits hit new highs. The company also advanced its debt reduction strategy by announcing a US$1.25 billion private offering of senior unsecured notes, aiming to replace higher-cost debt and further strengthen its financial position.
